Born in the Echoes is the eighth album by English electronic dance music duo The
Chemical Brothers, released on 17 July 2015 by record label Virgin EMI - It was
their first studio album since 2010's Further...

The album's first single, "Sometimes I Feel So Deserted", was released on 21 April 2015
The second single, "Go", was released on 5 May."Under Neon Lights" was released as the
third single on 23 June 2015, and features St - Vincent, credited by her real name
(Annie Clark) on vocals.The album was released on 17 July 2015
